name: visão além do alcance (vision beyond reach)
description: 'vision beyond reach' - photography and digital illustration - I work with multiple image and sound manipulation tools, and for some years now I have been developing visual works based on this universe / character that I usually call "star look" or visuals related to stars. This work starts an exclusive series that I am developing for hic et nunc. If you are interested in knowing more about me, be sure to look for me, let's talk.
